{"tid":861792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一個仆街兄弟姊妹","createTime":"2018-10-14T11:44:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T13:52:18.000Z","uid":60171,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5c369a45168be7981213dfc2516a5b9480ea4198","tid":861792,"uid":60171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T11:44:04.000Z","msg":"女朋友有個好on9嘅細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話說今日去佢屋企煮飯，所以開左煤氣制<br />\n食完洗曬野就兩個岀去行下<br />\n但行到半路醒起未閂煤氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n女朋友咪想打電話提佢細佬熄煤氣，但佢細佬係完全唔會聽佢電話，連老豆老母都係<br />\n我聽到真係屌岀聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢個死人腦係咪裝屎<br />\n電話都唔撚聽，咁部電話除左上網攞嚟把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 上網用電腦，部電話掟岀街啦<br />\n如果真係發生咩事打去揾佢又唔撚聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n平時都知佢個人古古怪怪，好難相處，好少講野<br />\n<br />\n但今日聽到真係覺得離曬譜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n諗到再講"},{"pid":"ac527c4fb667c5c56e1dffa94a9038cc641156a7","tid":861792,"uid":49669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T11:50:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa0bea6cfadd67ef665525c35b90837caab8e8e","tid":861792,"uid":60171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T12:28:47.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2315966872cfc6a9407d11bd1924e82e8063dac","tid":861792,"uid":60171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T12:28:59.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/asse